                            Label: "burn_charter_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "Third ledger. A charter page, foundational. There is a signature line and the name has been scrubbed to a clean blank - like they took a hot iron to it. And there, by the quench, is the man they sent to collect the last shipment. He will not start anything. Your move."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "The charter page - and the collector",
                    Label: "burn_three"
                }
            ]
